🔹 🎯 Task: Random Number Guess Result

📥 Inputs:
int userGuess;   // number from 1 to 10

⚙️ Requirements:
Generate a random number between 1 and 10
Compare it with userGuess

Print:
"Exact match! You win" → if equal
"Close!" → if difference is 1
"Wrong guess" → otherwise

📤 Example:
Random number: 7
Your guess: 6
Close!